:+1: but it should still be safe in case the multiple use fixer is not run before though. Is it the case ?

---------------------------------------------------------------------------

by keradus at 2014-09-02T19:27:54Z

Yes. You can run only OrderedUse.

But - if OrderedUse will be run before MultipleUse then:
* original:
```php
use A;
use B, D;
use C;
```
* after OrderedUse:
no changes
* after MultipleUse
```php
use A;
use B;
use D;
use C;
```

Which is not so ordered ;)

